game.name: Stickman School Run
game.description:
The lovely stickman has suddenly realized that his love is waiting for him in school. However, he is already a bit late and pretty sure that this hero would get late again to meet his girlfriend today. He cannot be reached until he performs multiple activities over the platform. Join Stickman School Run and be prepared to help your heroic character reach his love in time! Remember she is already very angry with him and ready to make a breakup with his boy if he fails in reaching timely. 

You are the best friend of Stickman and make him believe that he will meet his love again in school. Put your fingers on the arrow keys of the mouse or tap the screen and get ready to control your friend to find his love and have some romantic hours together! Try to grab all stars you see on his way to complete each level with good score in this brand new adventure game! He does not want to attempt this homework now and is looking forward to get in touch with his girlfriend. 

Test your running and jumping abilities to complete each level with the maximum stars possible! There are 100 unique and challenging levels to play through and 300 stars to collect in this HTML5 running game! Good luck to give him until he reaches the end in each level! Avoid the difficulties that are coming to you and make sure to help him jump one platform to another without falling into pitfall! Levels become harder when you progress in the game. Check out more top popular games that are free to play online without download!
